#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:180
msgid "About MTU"
msgstr "关于MTU"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:175
msgid ""
"All modern network program will determe TCP and UDP MTU size for themselfs "
"even if there is \"Path MTU Blackhole\", so it's ok to have default MTU "
"value 1500 on Ethernet adapter"
msgstr ""
"即使网络中存在“路径MTU黑洞（Path MTU Blackhole）”所有现代网络程序也能自动为"
"TCP和UDP协议探测MTU尺寸，在网卡上使用默认MTU值1500不会有什么问题"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:86
msgid "Apply"
msgstr "应用"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:94
msgid "Close"
msgstr "关闭"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:72
msgid "Help"
msgstr "帮助"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:177
msgid ""
"In theory, path mtu discovey is not an optional feature of IPv6 protocol "
"compare to IPv4 DF flag, either applications and internet service provider "
"must support Path MTU Discovery in IPv6 (RFC 8201). However, poor web server "
"maintainer may decide to block all ICMP protocols to improve their server's "
"security, so called \"Path MTU Blackhole\". It's a pretty questionable "
"choice because this may cause some IPv6 applications to use 1280 (RFC 2460) "
"as their MTU when path MTU discovery can't be performed, which reduces "
"network performance"
msgstr ""
"理论上，与IPv4的可选DF标记（DF flag）相比，路径MTU发现（path mtu discovery）"
"不是IPv6的可选功能，应用程序或互联网服务提供方必须在IPv6中支持路径MTU发现"
"（RFC 8201）。然而固执的Web服务器维护人员可能决定为了提升他们服务器的安全性而"
"禁止所有ICMP协议，这个现象称为“路径MTU黑洞（Path MTU Blackhole）”。这个决定的"
"问题在于当路径MTU发现无法执行，可能导致部分IPv6应用直接使用1280作为MTU值"
"（RFC 2460），导致网络性能下降"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:213
msgid "Invalid IP address or domain"
msgstr "无效的IP地址或域名"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:51
msgid "MTU measure fail"
msgstr "MTU测量失败"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:173
msgid ""
"On Windows, your IPv4 MTU value is measured by using IPv4 DF flag, IPv6 MTU "
"is minus 20 from this value. There is no easy way to measure IPv6 MTU "
"directly on Windows platform"
msgstr ""
"在Windows系统上，IPv4的MTU值通过IPv4 DF标记（DF flag）检测，IPv6的MTU值在此基"
"础上减去20。在Windows系统上没有简单的方法来直接检测IPv6的MTU值"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:15
msgid "Optimize MTU"
msgstr "优化MTU"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:171
msgid ""
"Optimize MTU function only meaningful if there is \"Path MTU Blackhole\" or "
"tinc can't perform IPv4 Path MTU Discovery automatically on your system"
msgstr ""
"优化MTU功能仅在存在“路径MTU黑洞（Path MTU Blackhole）”时，或是tinc无法在你的"
"系统上自动执行IPv4 路径MTU发现（Path MTU Discovery）时有意义"

